{"tid":85132,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[iOS/AN] 格林筆記","createTime":"2017-01-18T05:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T23:46:01.000Z","uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0064a97be77c31caedb985548d6a71733bdd18d","tid":85132,"uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:53:51.000Z","msg":"唔知有無人玩<br />\n用返以前個post d資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/m374712b34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fm374712b34.jpg&h=f20ac075&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/u75063q163.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fu75063q163.jpg&h=0a262d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 我誕生於世，被賦予了一本書<br />\n-以RPG呈現主角協同配角所主導著空白的劇本-<br />\n我與生俱來，<br />\n是一本書賦予的<br />\n我的世界，生命的意義，命運。<br />\n將一切紀下的劇本，<br />\n『命運之書』<br />\n全知的存在，說書人啊<br />\n遵從著那本『命運之書』<br />\n我至始至終，<br />\n將無止盡的扮演『命運之書』中的角色<br />\n屬於著這個世界不變的生活方式<br />\n是的，你將是告訴我<br />\n『命運之書』空白的每一頁<br />\n那賦予劇情之人<br />\n究竟將扮演什麼樣的命運呢<br />\n我不知道我應該如何活著？<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.grimmsnotes.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.grimmsnotes.jp%2F&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a5df6f4b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.grimmsnotes.jp/</a><br />\nFAQ環節:<br />\nQ. 邊隻五星起手好?<br />\nA. 除左補難D起手之外 其他都好<br />\nQ. 點先有三粒珠<br />\nA. 起超必殺研究所<br />\nQ. 單人曜日中間粒星點解<br />\nA. 特定Leader通關 睇後面個名黎對番<br />\nQ. 十連定單抽好<br />\nA. 運氣, 順帶一提起手要刷十連大約要推兩個島<br />\nQ. 好友follow姐係點<br />\nA.<br />\n睇你自己用開邊三個主角,隊友只會用剩低個個<br />\nQ. 有乜野野必起<br />\nA. 素材倉*3, 主堡LV5, 必殺研究所, 武器研究所<br />\nQ. 主線邊到可以打料升建/升建要咩料?<br />\nA. <a href=\"http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29627&amp;snA=362&amp;tnum=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29627%26snA%3D362%26tnum%3D17&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=89e5ea04\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29627&amp;snA=362&amp;tnum=17</a><br />\nQ. 主堡點解要升咁高<br />\nA. LV2 可以開連擊, LV3 開協力, LV4 可以交換素材, LV5開多幅地<br />\nQ. 切換技點用<br />\nA. Combo個陣換人就得, 要用一粒必殺<br />\nQ. __素材要邊到搵<br />\nA. 開倉庫, 點個舊素材可以知道邊到有得打<br />\nQ. 升素材倉既綠/藍碎邊到有得打<br />\nA. 綠=3島, 藍=5島<br />\nQ. 聽講曜日有素材打<br />\nA.<br />\n月曜日(星期一):銅/ミスリル秘銀(藍色既)/暗石/忍耐符文<br />\n火曜日(星期二):銀/ルビー紅寶石/火石/正義符文<br />\n水曜日(星期三):鐵/サファイア藍寶石/水石/慎重符文<br />\n木曜日(星期四):木頭/エメラルド綠寶石/雷石/希望符文<br />\n金曜日(星期五):金/ダイヤ鑽石,金剛石/光石/慈愛符文<br />\n土曜日(星期六):EXP/節制符文<br />\n日曜日(星期日):錢/誠實符文<br />\nQ. 除左片手劍仲有冇3*打?<br />\nA.<br />\n島5 有2*武器製作圖,<br />\n島4 有3*武器進化圖(要由2*進化上去),<br />\n島5果隻武係冇得升去3星同埋賣到4個銀幣<br />\n3*武以上要交換銀幣先整到<br />\nQ. 銀幣點拎?<br />\nA. 賣武器 (1*=1, 2*=3) / 核心core<br />\nQ. 進化材料係邊到打<br />\nA. 曜日關卡, 其他日子開既曜日關卡可以用2石開1個鐘比你打<br />\nQ. 信箱有冇上限?<br />\nA. 有! 得100封, 多左既會刪, 記得定時清<br />\nQ. 武器屬性<br />\nA.<br />\n片手劍 - 斬<br />\n太刀 - 斬&amp;打<br />\n盾鎚/斧 - 打<br />\n盾矛 - 突<br />\n單手杖 - 魔<br />\n書 - 魔<br />\n雙手杖 - 魔<br />\n弓 - 突<br />\nQ. 比怪屈到起唔到身<br />\nA. 可以擊飛期間出技無敵 / 上/下移<br />\nQ. 抽唔到五星得雙四星開唔開波好？<br />\nQ. 唔撚抽啦，有無咩四星好用？<br />\nQ. 得一隻五星，有邊隻四星好用？<br />\n<br />\nA. 以下為現版本全四星名單，現階段每隻都有特色每隻都好用，自己憑職種 + 花名認人，認唔到真係幫你唔到。<br />\n【】內為被動技、『』為值得特別介紹既特有必殺、<span style=\"color: red;\">紅字</span>為特別推薦，上五星、六星再限突真係完全唔輸蝕。"},{"pid":"04c8047ef2b8b49151dbfeaf23e3d136f8d7a6e1","tid":85132,"uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"片手劍（男）<br />\n火劍【火攻+10%】【背後減傷20%】<br />\n阿拉丁【30%血以下時+30%攻】【過關後金錢15%Up】<br />\n<br />\n片手劍（女）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">鬼姬【殺敵+1%攻，Cap 30%】【攻擊敵人背後+ 20%攻】<br />\n</span><br />\n大劍（男）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">船長【素材掉落率+10%】【擊暈】</span><br />\n<br />\n大劍（女）<br />\n大波櫻耶 【必殺技+20%攻】【30%血以下時+30%攻】<br />\n金髮雙馬尾【20 Combo後+20%攻】【過關後武器Exp15%Up】<br />\n<br />\n槍盾（男）<br />\n唐吉 【格檔】【攻擊滿血敵人+40%攻】<br />\n<br />\n槍盾（女）<br />\n金甲妹 【格檔】【20 Combo後+20%攻】<br />\n<br />\n槌盾（男）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">薯條肥仔（肥宅）【格檔】【過關後武器Exp15%Up】『必殺為我方全體+防』</span><br />\n<br />\n槌盾（女）<br />\n綠毛妹【格檔】【雷攻+10%】<br />\n<br />\n雙手杖（男）<br />\n吉爾（元帥，紅毛）【雷攻+10%】【入場時必殺滿兩珠】<br />\n瘋帽【20 Combo後+20%攻】【光攻+10%】<br />\n<br />\n雙手杖（女）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">娃娃法（異色曈）【遠距離時+20%攻】【攻擊滿血敵人+40%攻】『必殺為範圍隕石』</span><br />\n腹肌黑妹（其實係隻馬）【暗攻+10%】【火攻+10%】<br />\n三月兔【暗攻+10%】【毒效果（被敵人擊中時機率上毒）】<br />\n冰女王【冰攻+10%】【冰防+10%】<br />\n<br />\n單手杖（男）<br />\n無<br />\n<br />\n單手杖（女）<br />\n懷表兔【靜止時身邊隊友回血】【入場時必殺滿兩珠】<br />\n粉毛蘿莉 【靜止時身邊隊友回血】【暗防+10%】<br />\n<br />\n弓（男）<br />\n羅賓漢【遠距離時+攻】【每Wave開始時+攻5%（上限30%）】<br />\n金銀島細路【移動速度+10%】【30%血以下時+30%攻】<br />\n<br />\n弓（女）<br />\n無<br />\n<br />\n魔導書（男）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">軟飯王（死TB / 吉爾達條仔）【冰攻+10%】【每Wave開始時一名最少血角色Hp 30%回復】『必殺為敵方全員減攻』</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魔導書（女）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大波魔女 【20 Combo後+20%攻】【Exp +15%】『必殺為我方全體+攻』</span><br />\n見好似有巴打 唔知開左波之後到底要玩乜 講下起手流程先 <br />\n<br />\n5*起手派: <br />\n推到5島, 然後邊推島邊做以下既野 (最好升到幾lv) <br />\n起武器研究所(3), 必殺技研究所(愈高愈好), 掘素材機(無所謂), 主城(5), 素材倉庫(愈高愈好, 5島先起到) <br />\n主城2lv unlock combo技, 最好D角色20lv左右就入去開哂佢 會加普攻連擊數 <br />\n第三次解鎖切換技 (角色普攻緊個陣換人就會出, 用1粒必殺球) <br />\n主城3lv unlock 協力 可以同人打曜日關(抱大腿打超級都得) <br />\n可以快速升下LV, 提升成隊實力, 同埋可以刷特定素材去升建築 呢個下面再整理 <br />\n武器方面 1島會比一把3*水劍, 初期建議大家係5島過關拎既2*武器製作書到整2*武升3* <br />\n因為銀幣係一個好撚大既坑黎 冇時間盡量最後先掂 <br />\n<br />\n另外曜日可以用2石unlock1個鐘, 可以用黎farm 進化素材 個人prefer個重點應該放係 <br />\n5*未滿LV前盡量升素材倉(333) -&gt; 6* -&gt; 7* -&gt; 搞到素材倉666lv -&gt; 最尾先搞銀幣武器 (3*-&gt;4*武器) <br />\n<br />\n對應曜日應該去搞既素材 (lv5前) <br />\n月: 大量銅(小中大) <br />\n火: 火之石(小) (超必殺研究所), 紅寶石 <br />\n水: 藍寶石(素材倉) <br />\n木: 綠寶石(素材倉) <br />\n金: 金塊(升主城), 光之石(小) (升超必殺研究所) <br />\n<br />\n大約係咁 各位巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">D女女好唔好J?</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/d152822w34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fd152822w34.jpg&h=d531d685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s26.postimg.org/4xb3sc1hj/0001318592.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2F4xb3sc1hj%2F0001318592.jpg&h=3844874e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/x130292z34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fx130292z34.jpg&h=2adf7e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/i499172r34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fi499172r34.jpg&h=4e048c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/q2723Screensh4-47q128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fq2723Screensh4-47q128.jpg&h=9b76d7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/n49469Screensh4-55x128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fn49469Screensh4-55x128.jpg&h=030bdcdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/01/25/225017_e8258c87959ed6e94f12d6e4b19a726a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F01%2F25%2F225017_e8258c87959ed6e94f12d6e4b19a726a.jpg&h=3b0feb3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/01/25/225022_f09eb227bb4d69a0f4489749aa9550f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F01%2F25%2F225022_f09eb227bb4d69a0f4489749aa9550f9.jpg&h=24766e40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/01/25/225028_c6538f61780e5b3ef0978181ae064797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F01%2F25%2F225028_c6538f61780e5b3ef0978181ae064797.jpg&h=de5c4601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n角色起源介紹<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29627&amp;amp;snA=448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D29627%26amp%3BsnA%3D448&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=67607340\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=29627&amp;amp;snA=448</a><br />\n<strong>開post跟依到</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sbKAMYgmzeLZr4u093a_UUCYiNyMJACUP7Ra_a1Vtrg/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1sbKAMYgmzeLZr4u093a_UUCYiNyMJACUP7Ra_a1Vtrg%2Fedit&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=283e15e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sbKAMYgmzeLZr4u093a_UUCYiNyMJACUP7Ra_a1Vtrg/edit</a><br />\n跟分界線停"},{"pid":"387dc2c30e374432d0b7422ae1c6ad3cd0f57e84","tid":85132,"uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:56:30.000Z","msg":"而家d角應該係跟一周年個pool 抽就最好<br />\n<br />\n想刷既可以睇海鮮網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://appmedia.jp/grimm_notes/198512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fappmedia.jp%2Fgrimm_notes%2F198512&d=cHmYZd2m65yKt2yIaIL4O3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=54f6ba79\" target=\"_blank\">appmedia.jp/grimm_notes/198512</a>"},{"pid":"0feb4479c7157aceeda6902c71c30a09743cf9c0","tid":85132,"uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbb71e0af994ada4f2cac29982dd1cbcad0a02b","tid":85132,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:00:09.000Z","msg":"已經無撚晒人啦 仲玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4a6b43f576e2350cda47589811d4d517c3aa7b","tid":85132,"uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經無撚晒人啦 仲玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下仲有無人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0734cf2dc8c79ae02b1344b23b04d51780b844c3","tid":85132,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:45:00.000Z","msg":"無哂人玩喇"},{"pid":"d2e28764d88c6c0392c9ddcedfeb571a8caf0abb","tid":85132,"uid":9984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"仲有人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6f4a62cfa2f72dab71d25a800792a023e499da8","tid":85132,"uid":71695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T02:38:21.000Z","msg":"登入有一個十連 而家出左兩隻限<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb9862e0ab78141c7a8e6f09281a591de2dad75","tid":85132,"uid":74963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T23:46:01.000Z","msg":"岩岩入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}